title._content: Chinese funeral on Main Street VPL 66980

description._content: DESCRIPTION: Chinese funeral procession on Westminster at Princess (now Main and Pender). The City Grocery Company at 450 Westminster is visible in the background. VPL Accession Number: 17064 Date: 1894 Photographer/Studio: Unknown SUBJECTS: Chinese - Funeral customs and rites, Funeral rites and ceremonies, Chinese Canadians Location: British Columbia - Vancouver - Main Street British Columbia - Vancouver - Pender Street More information on our historical photograph collection: www.vpl.ca/historicalphotos
